   "source": [
    "## Pertanyaan inti yang kita jawab\n",
    "- Seberapa besar tingkat kecemasan finansial Gen Z pada data ini?\n",
    "- Segmen mana yang paling perlu dibantu dulu (pekerjaan, tempat tinggal, pendidikan)?\n",
    "- Faktor apa yang paling berkaitan dengan kecemasan (impulsif, perencanaan, awareness risiko)?\n",
    "- Apakah ada perbedaan mencolok antar provinsi yang perlu perhatian?\n",
    "- Siapa profil pengguna kita (pendidikan, tempat tinggal) untuk menyesuaikan konten?\n",
    "- (Opsional) Apakah pendapatan berkorelasi dengan kecemasan jika datanya memungkinkan?"
   ]
  },

   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "7fb318c0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Import dan setup dasar\n",
    "import os, json, warnings, subprocess\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib\n",
    "# Gunakan backend inline agar grafik tampil di notebook\n",
    "matplotlib.use('module://matplotlib_inline.backend_inline')\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "from IPython.display import display\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "def find_repo_root(start: str | None = None):\n",
    "    start = start or os.getcwd()\n",
    "    # 1) coba git\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        root = subprocess.check_output(['git', 'rev-parse', '--show-toplevel'], cwd=start, stderr=subprocess.DEVNULL).decode().strip()\n",
    "        return root\n",
    "    except Exception:\n",
    "        pass\n",
    "    # 2) jalan ke atas cari .git atau folder DATASET\n",
    "    p = Path(start).resolve()\n",
    "    for parent in [p] + list(p.parents):\n",
    "        if (parent / '.git').exists() or (parent / 'DATASET').exists():\n",
    "            return str(parent)\n",
    "    # 3) fallback: pakai cwd\n",
    "    return start\n",
    "\n",
    "base = find_repo_root()\n",
    "DATA = os.path.join(base, 'DATASET')\n",
    "fig_dir = os.path.join(base, 'notebooks', 'figures')\n",
    "os.makedirs(fig_dir, exist_ok=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "def read_csv_any(path):\n",
    "    for enc in ['utf-8', 'utf-8-sig', 'latin-1']:\n",
    "        try:\n",
    "            return pd.read_csv(path, encoding=enc, sep=';')\n",
    "        except UnicodeDecodeError:\n",
    "            continue\n",
    "    return pd.read_csv(path, engine='python', sep=';')\n",
    "\n",
    "profile = read_csv_any(os.path.join(DATA, 'GenZ_Financial_Profile.csv'))\n",
    "# Buat indeks kecemasan finansial (rata-rata beberapa item negatif jika ada)\n",
    "anx_items = [\n",
    "    'Because of my money situation, I feel I will never have the things I want in life',\n",
    "    'I am behind with my finances',\n",
    "    'My finances control my life',\n",
    "    'Whenever I feel in control of my finances, something happens that sets me back',\n",
    "    'I am unable to enjoy life because I obsess too much about money'\n",
    "]\n",
    "cols = [c for c in anx_items if c in profile.columns]\n",
    "if cols:\n",
    "    profile['financial_anxiety_score'] = profile[cols].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce').mean(axis=1)\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    # fallback: gunakan kolom yang mengandung kata 'anxiety' jika ada\n",
    "    anx_guess = [c for c in profile.columns if 'anxiety' in c.lower()]\n",
    "    profile['financial_anxiety_score'] = profile[anx_guess].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce').mean(axis=1) if anx_guess else np.nan\n",
    "\n",
    "# Upaya sederhana mendeteksi kolom impulsif & awareness risiko (berdasarkan nama kolom)\n",
    "imp_cols = [c for c in profile.columns if any(k in c.lower() for k in ['impuls', 'impulsive'])]\n",
    "risk_cols = [c for c in profile.columns if any(k in c.lower() for k in ['risk', 'fintech', 'legal'])]\n",
    "def safe_mean(cols):\n",
    "    if not cols: return np.nan\n",
    "    return profile[cols].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce').mean(axis=1)\n",
    "profile['impulsivity_score'] = safe_mean(imp_cols)\n",
    "profile['risk_awareness_score'] = safe_mean(risk_cols)"
   ]
  },

    "## Panel 1: KPI (Ringkasan Cepat — apa yang dijawab dan kenapa penting)\n",

    "\n",
    "Apa yang dijawab oleh panel ini:\n",
    "- Seberapa tinggi rata-rata Financial Anxiety (skala 1–4).\n",
    "- Seberapa tinggi Impulsivity (jika tersedia).\n",
    "- Seberapa baik Digital Risk Awareness (jika tersedia).\n",
    "\n",
    "Mengapa penting: ini jadi kompas awal untuk semua orang sebelum menyelam ke detail.\n",
    "\n",
    "Bentuk saat ini: tabel sederhana di notebook.\n",
    "Bentuk di dashboard: kartu KPI besar dengan angka tebal, label jelas, dan keterangan singkat (mis. skala/arah baik-buruk).\n",
    "\n",
    "Cara baca:\n",
    "- Angka anxiety lebih tinggi = lebih cemas; target kita menurunkannya.\n",
    "- Bandingkan antar filter (mis. segmen atau provinsi) untuk melihat perubahan konteks."

    "## Panel 3: Drivers vs Anxiety (apa pemicunya)\n",
    "Pertanyaan yang dijawab: faktor mana yang paling berkaitan dengan kecemasan?\n",
    "\n",
    "Mengapa penting: dari sini lahir rekomendasi yang tepat (edukasi, fitur kontrol, dsb.).\n",
    "\n",
    "Bentuk saat ini: bar horizontal 8 faktor teratas berdasarkan korelasi Spearman (|rho| terbesar).\n",
    "Bentuk di dashboard: heatmap/daftar faktor yang dapat diklik untuk melihat contoh rekomendasi.\n",
    "\n",
    "Cara baca:\n",
    "- Nilai positif: faktor naik seiring kecemasan (calon pemicu).\n",
    "- Nilai negatif: faktor turun ketika kecemasan naik (calon pelindung)."
   ]

   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",

   ],
   "source": [
    "# Cari semua kolom numerik yang cukup terisi\n",
    "num_df = profile.apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='ignore')\n",
    "num_cols = [c for c in num_df.columns if pd.api.types.is_numeric_dtype(num_df[c]) and c != 'financial_anxiety_score']\n",
    "base = num_df[['financial_anxiety_score'] + num_cols].copy() if 'financial_anxiety_score' in num_df.columns else pd.DataFrame()\n",
    "if not base.empty:\n",
    "    # Spearman lebih aman untuk skala Likert\n",
    "    corr_vals = []\n",
    "    fa = pd.to_numeric(base['financial_anxiety_score'], errors='coerce')\n",
    "    for c in num_cols:\n",
    "        x = pd.to_numeric(base[c], errors='coerce')\n",
    "        valid = fa.notna() & x.notna()\n",
    "        if valid.sum() >= 100:\n",
    "            rho = fa[valid].corr(x[valid], method='spearman')\n",
    "            if pd.notna(rho):\n",
    "                corr_vals.append((c, rho))\n",
    "    if corr_vals:\n",
    "        # ambil 8 teratas berdasarkan nilai absolut\n",
    "        top = sorted(corr_vals, key=lambda t: abs(t[1]), reverse=True)[:8]\n",
    "        labels, vals = zip(*top)\n",
    "        plt.figure(figsize=(8, max(3, 0.3*len(top))))\n",
    "        sns.barplot(x=list(vals), y=list(labels), orient='h', palette='coolwarm', hue=list(vals), dodge=False, legend=False)\n",
    "        plt.axvline(0, color='black', lw=1)\n",
    "        plt.title('Top Drivers vs Anxiety (Spearman)')\n",
    "        plt.xlabel('Korelasi (−1 s/d +1)')\n",
    "        plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "        fig = plt.gcf()\n",
    "        display(fig)\n",
    "        plt.close(fig)\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print('Tidak ada pasangan variabel dengan data cukup untuk korelasi.')\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print('Skor anxiety tidak tersedia atau tidak numerik.')"
   ]

    "# Coba parsing sederhana income/expense jika tersedia (banyak yang berbentuk teks)\n",
    "def parse_money(s):\n",
    "    if pd.isna(s): return np.nan\n",
    "    ss = str(s).lower()\n",
    "    # tangkap angka mentah (tanpa titik/koma/spasi) – ini kasar, lebih baik mapping rentang di pipeline web\n",
    "    digits = ''.join(ch for ch in ss if ch.isdigit())\n",
    "    return pd.to_numeric(digits, errors='coerce')\n",
    "if 'Est. Monthly Income' in profile.columns:\n",
    "    profile['income_num'] = profile['Est. Monthly Income'].apply(parse_money)\n",
    "if {'income_num','financial_anxiety_score'}.issubset(profile.columns):\n",
    "    d = profile[['income_num','financial_anxiety_score']].dropna()\n",
    "    if len(d) > 50 and d['income_num'].nunique()>5:\n",
    "        plt.figure(figsize=(6,5))\n",
    "        sns.scatterplot(data=d, x='income_num', y='financial_anxiety_score', alpha=0.3)\n",
    "        plt.title('Anxiety vs Income (parsial)')\n",
    "        plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "        fig = plt.gcf()\n",
    "        display(fig)\n",
    "        plt.close(fig)\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print('Data income belum cukup numerik untuk scatter yang bermakna.')\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print('Kolom income atau anxiety tidak tersedia.')"
   ]
